scopecontent.p:
Includes materials related to the Committee on Appointment and Promotion (CAP) and
            related groups such as the Ad Hoc Criteria Committee. Materials include reports on the
            history of CAP; rationale for decisions made in creating and structuring CAP policy;
            policy drafts; correspondence and memoranda regarding the work of CAP and its
            decision-making process; notes on a proposed external review commmittee for CAP;
            criteria for CAP decisions; and other subjects.
